# How a Request Travels Through the Application

When a user visits:

```text
http://localhost:3000/products
```

the request follows this path:

```text
Browser / Flutter App
          │
          ▼
      server.js
          │
          ▼
       app.js
          │
          ▼
app.use("/products", productRoutes)
          │
          ▼
productRoutes.js
          │
          ▼
router.get("/")
          │
          ▼
JSON Response
```

